<li id="cite_note-18"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-18">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Dehaene, S., Cohen, L., Sigman, M., &amp; Vinckier, F. (2005). The neural code for written words: A proposal. Trends in Cognitive Sciences, 9(7), 335-341. doi:10.1016/j.tics.2005.004</span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-19"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-19">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Collignon, O., Voss, P., Lassonde, M., &amp; Lepore, F. (2009). Cross-modal plasticity for the spatial processing of sounds in visually deprived subjects. Experimental Brain research, 192(3), 343-358. doi:10.1007/s00221-008-1553-z</span>
</li>
</ol></div></div>
